Gooeypoo ? Yahoo that name is great Gaelad!

Well if you ever decide to venture into the Rodcet Nife again, give me a
tell, Im always looking for a adventure. I am sort of broke for now because
I was busy twinking Daevan, who is the "Super Twink" but that will change as
Tonight I begin my Power leveling of Nate and the money just rolls in again,
so until I get my Hi-Elven ass out of the E commons area, Ill be in Guk
trying to make some money and Levels:o)If you see me on, give me a tell even
if just to say Hi, and that goes for everyone on the Rodcet Nife.. I don't
bite, (well unless you want me to)

Nate Bites Gooeypoo on the leg
Gooeypoo shivers at the thought of messing with Nate
Nate grabs Gooeypoo and shows him how to two step :o)J/K (I dont know how to
do that)
